OL,5, A Northern Ireland corporate loophole  
OL,6, that is exploited by international     
OL,7, money launderers should be closed, MPs 
OL,8, have said.                             
OL,10,FAn investigation by BBC NI's Spotlight 
OL,11,Fprogramme has looked at the use of     
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland Limited Partnerships  
OL,13,F(NILPs) for money laundering.          
OL,15,FThe secretive companies can be set up  
OL,16,Fin seconds from anywhere in the world. 
OL,18,FHundreds have been created since       
OL,19,FScotland made regulatory changes       
OL,20,Fdisclosing the ownership of similar    
OL,21,Fentities there five years ago.         
